<li><a href="Walter_Alvarez" title="Walter Alvarez">Walter Alvarez</a> of the <a href="University_of_California_at_Berkeley" title="University of California at Berkeley" class="mw-redirect">University of California at Berkeley</a> in California, USA<sup id="cite_ref-tws2M42_9-10" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-tws2M42-9"><span>[</span>9<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
