<li>Lowell Gustafson of <a href="Villanova_University" title="Villanova University">Villanova University</a> in Pennsylvania, USA<sup id="cite_ref-tws2M42_9-13" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-tws2M42-9"><span>[</span>9<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>Barry Rodrigue of the <a href="University_of_Southern_Maine" title="University of Southern Maine">University of Southern Maine</a>, USA<sup id="cite_ref-tws2M42_9-14" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-tws2M42-9"><span>[</span>9<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
<li><a href="Graeme_Snooks" title="Graeme Snooks">Graeme Snooks</a> of the <a href="Australian_National_University" title="Australian National University">Australian National University</a>, and the Institute of Global Dynamic Systems, Canberra, Australia.</li>
<li>Pamela Benjamin<sup id="cite_ref-tws2M42_9-15" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-tws2M42-9"><span>[</span>9<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
